  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/c36d2ed02d8d2e0893484d1a94508cdc.avif?t=1773655374\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have you ever wanted to make a smoothie in your blender at home? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have you had trouble fitting all the fruit in there?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Look no more with this top-of-the-line blender simulator using our <i>NASA APPROVED*</i> physics simulator. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No more shall you spill the fruit (of labor) as you try and try again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simulate your perfect smoothie in one of our three (3) gamemodes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/5874274b21c7c6bcbd780485fbbceba0.avif?t=1773655374\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classic Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop your fruit whenever you want where ever you want, Match fruit of the same type and they'll combine into the next level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You lose when a fruit escapes the blender.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/e5037e606dabbbe5f6db2512f7fd1233.avif?t=1773655374\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Attack!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic mode just got a little faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race the timer and match fruit to keep yourself from timing out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you handle the pressure of a full blender and 10 seconds on the clock?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/8d6cee741c5546d7b0d71732554d0dc5.avif?t=1773655374\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Auto Drop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It seems your spacebar got stuck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Autodrop constantly forces you to drop fruit at constantly increasing rates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planning & Structure go out the blender fast when the cherries rain from above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/2aba47a3a5183dca16890bc72f026b71.avif?t=1773655374\" alt=\"Super Fruit\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Super Fruit</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every so often. One of them shows up. A \"Super Fruit\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dread it, Run from it. It'll arrive in your queue all the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Gravity</strong></i> defying? <i><strong>Flattening</strong></i>? You'll get <i><strong>stuck</strong></i> to these fruit all the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So <i><strong>Bounce</strong></i> right back into this mode and pray, pray to anything that you'll be spared by them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And even when you think you're safe... It might just be a <i><strong>Chameleon</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* nasa did not aprove any of this and for legal reasons it's a joke.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/c36d2ed02d8d2e0893484d1a94508cdc.avif?t=1773655374\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have you ever wanted to make a smoothie in your blender at home? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have you had trouble fitting all the fruit in there?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Look no more with this top-of-the-line blender simulator using our <i>NASA APPROVED*</i> physics simulator. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No more shall you spill the fruit (of labor) as you try and try again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simulate your perfect smoothie in one of our three (3) gamemodes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/5874274b21c7c6bcbd780485fbbceba0.avif?t=1773655374\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classic Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop your fruit whenever you want where ever you want, Match fruit of the same type and they'll combine into the next level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You lose when a fruit escapes the blender.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/e5037e606dabbbe5f6db2512f7fd1233.avif?t=1773655374\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Attack!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic mode just got a little faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race the timer and match fruit to keep yourself from timing out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you handle the pressure of a full blender and 10 seconds on the clock?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/8d6cee741c5546d7b0d71732554d0dc5.avif?t=1773655374\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Auto Drop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It seems your spacebar got stuck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Autodrop constantly forces you to drop fruit at constantly increasing rates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planning & Structure go out the blender fast when the cherries rain from above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707420/extras/2aba47a3a5183dca16890bc72f026b71.avif?t=1773655374\" alt=\"Super Fruit\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Super Fruit</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every so often. One of them shows up. A \"Super Fruit\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dread it, Run from it. It'll arrive in your queue all the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Gravity</strong></i> defying? <i><strong>Flattening</strong></i>? You'll get <i><strong>stuck</strong></i> to these fruit all the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So <i><strong>Bounce</strong></i> right back into this mode and pray, pray to anything that you'll be spared by them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And even when you think you're safe... It might just be a <i><strong>Chameleon</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* nasa did not aprove any of this and for legal reasons it's a joke.</p>",
